{{Quote|Concurrently, I'll be dispatching elements of the Third Fleet to Coruscant from the Shawken Spur of the Hydian, and elements of the Fourth by way of the Martial Cross.|Traest Kre'fey, to [[Wedge Antilles/Legends|Wedge Antilles]]|<ref name="TUF">''[[The New Jedi Order: The Unifying Force]]''</ref>}}
The '''Shawken Spur''' was an ancient branch of the [[Hydian Way/Legends|Hydian Way]] connecting [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] and [[Shawken]]. It was one of the [[Hyperspace route/Legends|hyperspace routes]] used by [[Admiral/Legends|Admiral]] [[Traest Kre'fey]] for the [[Battle of Yuuzhan'tar|invasion of Coruscant]] that came at the end of the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]].

